title: Australia Election 2025: Anthony Albanese Sworn In As PM, Labor Government Gets Second Term
snippet: Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese was sworn in for a second term on Tuesday, alongside his ministers, after a landslide win at a national election he said had returned the largest centre-left Labor government since federation in 1901.
